insect.coverage.execution
Class BranchMonitor

java.lang.Object
  insect.coverage.execution.BranchMonitor
public class BranchMonitor
extends java.lang.Object

Provides methods for instrumented programs to report values evaluated in conditional branches during runtime. These methods simulate the evaluation of each condition in order to record branch coverage.

Author:
Anil Chawla
